_july_2023.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="houshou_marine_youtube_channel_30_july_2023" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/houshou_marine_youtube_channel_30_july_2023.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/houshou_marine_youtube_channel_30_july_2023.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/houshou_marine_youtube_channel_30_july_2023.png" alt="海军 Ch. Hosho Marine" class="wp-image-97985"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Marine Ch. Hosho Marine（截至 2023 年 7 月 30 日）<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>人才名称</td><td>注册人数（较1个月前增减）</td></tr><tr><td>宝生海洋</td><td>252 万 (+80,000)</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">截至2023年8月4日00:00 </figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="LRMyoLdF5b"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/houshou-marine-is-the-first-active-japanese-vtuber-to-reach-2-5-million-youtube-subscribers/">Hosho Marine 生日当天订阅人数突破 250 万，成为日本首位活跃 VTuber</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Hosho Marine 成为日本第一位在生日当天订阅人数达到 250 万的活跃 VTuber” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/houshou-marine-is-the-first-active-japanese-vtuber-to-reach-2-5-mill